=== Tarzan ===
[[File:Tarzan_ribbon.PNG|thumb|''The "Tarzan" ribbon.'']]
''Bond with exotic animals''

Difficulty: Varies

It is a orange-yellow tiger skin ribbon represented with tiger emoji. You have to be born as a male or be a transgender male to get this ribbon.

Procedures to get the ''Tarzan'' ribbon:
* Be a male.
* Have under millions of net worth without any debts.
* Buy exotic pets from the exotic pet dealer.
